org.codehaus.groovy.grails.web.mapping
Interface UrlMappingInfo

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractUrlMappingInfo, DefaultUrlMappingInfo
public interface UrlMappingInfo

The UrlMappingInfo interface defines that data that was produced when matching a URI with a UrlMapping instance.

Since:
0.5

Created: Feb 28, 2007 Time: 5:56:38 PM

Author:
Graeme Rocher

Method Detail

getURI

String getURI()
The URI to map to. Note when the URI is specified it overrides any explicit controller/action/id mappings. In other words you can either specify the URI or the controller/action/id, but not both

Returns:
